---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Joe Cardoso" description="About Joe Cardoso - Software Engineer specializing in observability and full-stack development">
  <h1>$ whoami</h1>
  
  <section class="about-content">
    <p>
      Hey! I'm Joe, a full-stack software engineer based in Toronto, Canada. I build systems that help developers understand what their code is doing in production.
    </p>

    <h2>Background</h2>
    <p>
    I have a Master of Engineering in Mechanical Engineering from Texas A&M and transitioned into software development after working with MatLab projects in school and finding out the joy of writing software. I have mastered Ruby, JavaScript and Python programming languages, along with all the fundamentals of Web Development. I'm particularly interested in observability, system performance, and contributing to Open Source in a meaningful way.
    </p>

    <h2>Current work</h2>
    <p>
    Right now I'm contributing to Mozilla Firefox, having landed a few patches with more in the pipeline. Claude Code has been paramount in augmenting my Software Engineering capabilities, allowing me to produce high quality software solutions at such an incredible pace. I also built <a href="https://vispyr.com">Vispyr</a>, an open-source observability tool that combines continuous profiling with traditional telemetry data.
    </p>

    <!-- <h2>Outside of code</h2> -->
    <!-- <p> -->
    <!--   When I'm not at the keyboard, you'll find me reading about AI and machine learning, playing guitar, or exploring how systems work at scale. I'm fascinated by the intersection of developer experience and system reliability. -->
    <!-- </p> -->

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <div class="contact-links">
      <a href="https://github.com/JoeCardoso13" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/joe-cardoso-eng" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="mailto:joe13_122@yahoo.com">Email</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .contact-links {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
